{"data":{"properties":{"created_at":1632104977000,"events":{},"identifier":"display/badge","modified_at":1632104977000,"properties":{"Badge":[{"name":"palette","description":"<p>Alters the displayed color scheme.</p>\n","types":["auto","inverse","inherit","accent","dark","light","alert","affirmative","negative"]},{"name":"position","description":"<p>Sets higher positioning on the <code>Badge</code>.</p>\n","types":["floated","raised"]}]},"sections":[{"identifier":"badge","level":1,"text":"Badge"},{"identifier":"imports","level":2,"text":"Imports"},{"identifier":"palette","level":2,"text":"Palette"},{"identifier":"position","level":2,"text":"Position"}],"snippets":[{"identifier":"badge-preview","script":"<script>\n    import {Badge} from \"@kahi-ui/framework\";\n</script>\n\n<Badge>This is a Badge!</Badge>","syntax":"svelte","title":"Badge Preview"},{"identifier":"badge-imports","script":"<script>\n    import {Badge} from \"@kahi-ui/framework\";\n</script>","syntax":"html","title":"Badge Imports"},{"identifier":"badge-palette","script":"<script>\n    import {Badge, Stack} from \"@kahi-ui/framework\";\n</script>\n\n<Stack\n    spacing=\"medium\"\n    orientation=\"horizontal\"\n    variation=\"wrap\"\n>\n    <Badge>This is a DEFAULT Badge</Badge>\n\n    <Badge palette=\"accent\">\n        This is a ACCENT Badge\n    </Badge>\n\n    <Badge palette=\"dark\">This is a DARK Badge</Badge>\n\n    <Badge palette=\"light\">\n        This is a LIGHT Badge\n    </Badge>\n\n    <Badge palette=\"alert\">\n        This is a ALERT Badge\n    </Badge>\n\n    <Badge palette=\"affirmative\">\n        This is a AFFIRMATIVE Badge\n    </Badge>\n\n    <Badge palette=\"negative\">\n        This is a NEGATIVE Badge\n    </Badge>\n</Stack>","syntax":"svelte","title":"Badge Palette"},{"identifier":"badge-position","script":"<script>\n    import {\n        Badge,\n        Button,\n        Stack,\n        Text,\n    } from \"@kahi-ui/framework\";\n</script>\n\n<Stack spacing=\"medium\">\n    <Text>\n        Sample Text (RAISED)\n        <Badge palette=\"accent\" position=\"raised\">\n            +99\n        </Badge>\n    </Text>\n\n    <div>\n        <Button palette=\"accent\">\n            Open Inbox (FLOATED)\n            <Badge\n                palette=\"negative\"\n                position=\"floated\"\n            >\n                +99\n            </Badge>\n        </Button>\n    </div>\n</Stack>","syntax":"svelte","title":"Badge Position"}],"title":"Badge"},"render":"<h1 id=\"badge\">Badge</h1>\n<p><code>Badge</code> is typically used to subtlely display to the user some type of ancillary information, relating to its siblings / parent UI elements.</p>\n<iframe\n    class=\"snippet-repl\"\n    src=\"/repl/docs/display/badge/badge-preview?rotation=horizontal\"\n    sandbox=\"allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-scripts allow-popups allow-forms allow-pointer-lock allow-top-navigation allow-modals allow-same-origin\" loading=\"lazy\"\n></iframe>\n<a href=\"/repl/docs/display/badge/badge-preview?rotation=horizontal\" hidden sveltekit:prefetch></a><h2 id=\"imports\">Imports</h2>\n<pre class=\"language-html snippet-highlight\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"><span class=\"token language-javascript\">\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>Badge<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@kahi-ui/framework\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre><h2 id=\"palette\">Palette</h2>\n<p>You can change the color palette of the <code>Badge</code> via the <code>palette</code> property.</p>\n<iframe\n    class=\"snippet-repl\"\n    src=\"/repl/docs/display/badge/badge-palette?rotation=horizontal\"\n    sandbox=\"allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-scripts allow-popups allow-forms allow-pointer-lock allow-top-navigation allow-modals allow-same-origin\" loading=\"lazy\"\n></iframe>\n<a href=\"/repl/docs/display/badge/badge-palette?rotation=horizontal\" hidden sveltekit:prefetch></a><h2 id=\"position\">Position</h2>\n<p>You can change the position of the <code>Badge</code> to raise it above in its parent to more explictly call out the information.</p>\n<iframe\n    class=\"snippet-repl\"\n    src=\"/repl/docs/display/badge/badge-position?rotation=horizontal\"\n    sandbox=\"allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-scripts allow-popups allow-forms allow-pointer-lock allow-top-navigation allow-modals allow-same-origin\" loading=\"lazy\"\n></iframe>\n<a href=\"/repl/docs/display/badge/badge-position?rotation=horizontal\" hidden sveltekit:prefetch></a>"}}